mixin Testimonials-2
	+Section#testimonials-2
		.row.justify-content-center
			.col-lg-10
				h3.mb-4 People talking about Slick

				.border.border-2.rounded-3.p-3.p-sm-4.p-lg-6.border-200#carouselTesitimonialtwo.carousel.slide.carousel-slider(data-bs-ride='carousel')
					.row.d-none.d-lg-block
						button.carousel-control-prev(type='button' data-bs-target='#carouselTesitimonialtwo' data-bs-slide='prev' style="transform: translate(-67px, -28px);")
							span.carousel-control-prev-icon(aria-hidden='true')
							span.visually-hidden prev
						button.carousel-control-next(type='button' data-bs-target='#carouselTesitimonialtwo' data-bs-slide='next'  style="transform: translate(67px, -28px);")
							span.carousel-control-next-icon(aria-hidden='true')
							span.visually-hidden Next	

					.carousel-inner
						.carousel-item.active
							.d-flex.align-items-start
								img(src=`${CWD}assets/img/portraits/square/10.jpg` alt="profile" style="width: 100px;").d-flex.me-2.me-md-3.mb-3.mb-sm-0.rounded-circle
								.flex-1.ps-sm-3
									p.lead.mb-4 I didn't know at first what's possible with Slick. When I found out I can create animation like Apple and without worrying about the code, I was surprised. This is truly remarkable. 
									h5.fs-0.mb-1 Tim Ferris
									p.fs--1.text-500.mb-0 Product Designer, Green Chameleon
						.carousel-item.h-100
							.d-flex.align-items-start
								img(src=`${CWD}assets/img/portraits/square/11.jpg` alt="profile" style="width: 100px;").d-flex.me-2.me-md-3.mb-3.mb-sm-0.rounded-circle
								.flex-1.ps-sm-3
									p.lead.mb-4 Prebuilt CSS helper classes made the editing HTML easier than before. I like the naming of the classes - intuitive and professional. Thanks to the awesome team behind Slick. 
									h5.fs-0.mb-1 Jessica Nulloy
									p.fs--1.text-500.mb-0 Creative Director, Fancy Web LLC
										
